item.title: CVE-2021-38337|2024-09-17T04:09:43.009Z -- rsvpmaker%20excel -- rsvpmaker%20excel
item.description: The RSVPMaker Excel WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting due to a reflected $_SERVER["PHP_SELF"] value in the ~/phpexcel/PHPExcel/Shared/JAMA/docs/download.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 1.1.
